# Cross-Project Calibration History
# Format: one JSON object per line, appended by the Retro phase after each project.
# Fields: project_id, date, telemetry_quality, work_type_multipliers, provider_multipliers, sample_sizes
# The Estimate phase reads this file and computes running averages for baseline calibration.
# Only entries with telemetry_quality "exact" or "estimated" should be appended.
